Quasar:




Quasar sat up, a little light headed at first, and watched the images 
on the screen. To a young Predacon's mind, it was nothing. She came 
from a line of warriors, and the scenes did nothing but show her war, 
something she was shown to at the first few moments of her time on-
line. 

She turned her head to Omnious. "Do you want something?" she said, 
looking non-impressed. Then she realized this was not an usual place. 
She never seen this bot before. "Hold up, who are you anyways?"
